

### curl request
/*
curl -X POST http://localhost:8082/api/v1/social/google \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "idToken": "YOUR_GOOGLE_ID_TOKEN",
    "deviceId": "device123",
    "deviceName": "iPhone 15"
  }'
*/
POST http://localhost:8082/api/v1/social/google
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "idToken": "YOUR_GOOGLE_ID_TOKEN",
    "deviceId": "device123",
    "deviceName": "iPhone 15"
  }

